# Production (main) = frozen V3

| Role | Path |
|------|------|
| Live HTML | `index.html` (do not edit on `main` except production hotfixes) |
| Copy | `copy/COPY-v3.md` (frozen on `main`) |
| Archive snapshot | `archive/v3/` |
| Git tag | `v3.0` |

## Active development (V4)

Check out branch **`v4`** before editing the site draft:

```bash
git checkout v4
```

On `v4`: edit `copy/COPY-v4.md` → apply to root `index.html`. Pushing `v4` does **not** change the live site. Merge to `main` only when ready to ship V4.

## Frozen / archive

| Version | HTML | Copy |
|---------|------|------|
| V3 | `archive/v3/index.html` | `copy/COPY-v3.md` |
| V2 | `archive/v2/index.html` | `copy/COPY-v2.md` |
| V1 | `archive/v1/index.html` | `copy/COPY-v1.md` |

## Redirects

- `/` → production (V3 on `main` until V4 ships)
- `/v3/` → `/archive/v3/`
- `/v2/` → `/archive/v2/`
- `/v1/` → `/archive/v1/`

## Conventions

- Spaced hyphen ` - ` in copy, not em dash
- Case study tags use middle dot ` · `
- Company name: Teradar (capital T only)
